#include<cstdio>
#define MAX(a,b) ((a) > (b) ? a : b)
#define MIN(a,b) ((a) < (b) ? a : b)
static int arr[10];
void calc(int x){
while(x>0){
arr[x%10]++;
x/=10;
}
return;
}

int a,b,i,c=1;

 return 0;

    arr[i]=0;

    for(i=MIN(a,b);i<=MAX(a,b);i++){
        calc(i);
    }

}
return 0;
}
